| table_type | Description |
|------------|-------------|
| obligations | Extract all obligations from documents |
| payments | Payment terms and schedules |
| timeline | Key dates and deadlines |
| responsibilities | Party responsibilities |
| defined_terms | Defined terms glossary |
| approvals | Approval requirements |
| risk_matrix | Risk assessment matrix |
| comparison | Document comparison table |
| compliance_gaps | Compliance gap analysis |
| deliverables | Deliverables tracking |
| renewals | Renewal dates and terms |
| notices | Notice requirements |
| indemnities | Indemnification provisions |
| liabilities | Liability provisions |
| custom | Custom column definitions |

**When to Use**:
- Structured analysis of legal documents
- Extracting specific data points
- Creating comparison matrices
- Building due diligence tables

**When NOT to Use**:
